          "text": "踢死御弟，乃一时酒醉，儿也曾绘影图形拿薛刚问罪。特求国母恩赦薛氏一门，\n那忠武王在九泉之下，感恩无尽矣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武则天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，你不诛父遗恨，容留叛逆，懦弱为君，怎掌天下大事？今废你为卢陵王，\n贬往湖广房州。若无旨意，不可擅入长安。将御印交出，速行去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李显",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，孩儿为君，并无失政，不过求赦忠良之心，为何将儿贬出长安？"
        },
        {
          "character": "武则天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，你无父王之仇，为娘哪有母子之意？\n内侍，快到韦后宫内，请御印前来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（太监下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "武则天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你即出长安。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李显",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，母后吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李显",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿为君非失政，\n为何谪贬出都城？\n大唐社稷付何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "今日奉诏泄母恨、母后吓、武则天",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为娘临朝比儿胜，\n汉室吕后女为君。\n可知成汤亡百春。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四宫女、二太监捧印引韦后同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "韦后",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主上为君如尧舜，\n为救薛氏一满门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韦后",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "国母千岁。进宫何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "武则天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主上柔弱，夫妻早出长安便罢，若是迟延，提头来见。\n内侍，快将他夫妻赶出去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李显、韦后",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀母后吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李显",
          "line_type": "西皮滚板",
          "musical_style": "西皮滚板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿承父业风雨顺，"
        },
        {
          "character": "韦后",
          "line_type": "西皮滚板",
          "musical_style": "西皮滚板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "人在尧天舜日中。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李显",
          "line_type": "西皮滚板",
          "musical_style": "西皮滚板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "国母废业社稷送，"
        },
        {
          "character": "韦后",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "国母吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "韦后",
          "line_type": "西皮滚板",
          "musical_style": "西皮滚板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "哀告膝下求乞恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武则天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，无用之辈，怎为天子，再不出宫，提头来见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李显",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李显",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "甜言蜜语全无用，"
        },
        {
          "character": "韦后",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再三哀告总是空。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李显",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李显",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大唐江山无我分，"
        },
        {
          "character": "韦后",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "眼含珠泪出皇宫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李显、韦后",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，国母吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李显、韦后同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "武则天",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "武则天",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "临朝执掌唐一统，\n女王天子独为君。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武则天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内侍，速传旨意：新君已废，本后登基，改元为垂拱元年。朝内大事，付与天\n佐、天佑执掌；命武三思统领都城禁军。打扫法场，将薛家满门正法；再命武\n承嗣，在丁山中殿上，掘一深坑，以便埋葬叛臣尸首。恐有文武保奏，谏者提\n头来见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二太监",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二太监同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "武则天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇儿已废，本后执掌江山，谁敢搭救薛氏满门！"
        },
        {
          "character": "武则天",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "称制重把山河整，\n一朝公卿换新君。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（武则天下。）"
        }
      ],
